cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning a model to distinguish between natural photographs and composite images based on visual realism. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) model to learn the perception of visual realism directly from data. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a model to classify images based on their realism. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with composite images and their perception of realism. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper involves analyzing and improving the visual quality of composite images.
